high_descs: Move to the microwave above the stove.
Grab the egg from within the microwave and close the door.
Move to the refrigerator on the left
Place the egg inside and close the door, let chill for a moment before removing the egg and closing the door again.
Move to the bin to the left
Put the egg in the bin
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled egg from the microwave into the bin.

high_descs: Take the egg out of the microwave.
Bring the egg to the fridge.
Chill the egg in the fridge.
Bring the chilled egg to the trash can.
Put the chilled egg in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg in the trash can.

high_descs: Open the microwave, take the egg out of the microwave, close the microwave
Turn around, and turn right, walk to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator, put the egg on the shelf, close the refrigerator, wait for a while, open the refrigerator, take the egg out, close the refrigerator
Turn left, walk to the end, turn left, walk to the trash bin
Put the egg in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Cool the egg in the refrigerator, throw the egg away in the trash bin
